### General Info
***

Backend for frontend. It has been developed to give access to suscripcionAdidas Microservice methods. 
There are 4 diferent methods:
"/adidas/createSubscription" -->
"/adidas/deleteSubscription/{id}" -->
"/adidas/subscriptions/{id}" -->
"/adidas/subscriptions" -->

## Technologies
***
A list of technologies used within the project:
* [spring-boot-starter-web]: Version 12.3 
* [spring-boot-devtools]: Version 2.34

## Installation
***
Running using docker.
Docker is an open platform for building, shipping and running distributed applications. Follow steps on the site to install docker based on your operating system.
Run the bffAdidas image as below:
*sudo docker run bffAdidas (suscripcionAdidas image should be run before this.)